# Implement vector similarity queries

Build Elixir API for vector similarity search using pgvector distance operators.

## Requirements

- [ ] Create VectorSearch context module
- [ ] Implement cosine similarity search
- [ ] Implement L2 distance search
- [ ] Add filtering by metadata
- [ ] Support top-k retrieval with configurable limit

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Can search by cosine similarity: `<=> operator`
- [ ] Can search by L2 distance: `<-> operator`
- [ ] Returns top-k most similar vectors
- [ ] Supports metadata filtering (JSONB queries)
- [ ] Unit tests verify search accuracy
- [ ] Performance acceptable for 10k+ vectors

